task.summary: Sphere parametrization fixed, GradientShader implemented & Solver for Quartic equations implemented
Mapping of phi fixed for spheres (finally...)
Light source position changed to match the direction of the z axis
API prepared for multi ray sampling
Helper class to calculate the field of view for a given film format and focal length
Restructuring of the scene readers in preparation for a more flexible architecture
Interface names changed to match the actual names
Blender scene for the first light scene added (including a collada export)
Directory after restructuring the scene reader package no longer needed (will be re-added in the proper place when there are actual tests)
Existing scene reader integrated in the new interface hierarchy
Hemisphere sampling included for epsilon as 0, 1, 512
Commandline argument for scene file added
Triangle intersection calculation implemented -> Not complete, error in test class
Removed failing tests due to the new rendering interface
Static imports for most used transformations added
Minor enhancements to the perspective camera
